{"tid":236732,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼撈麵世界第一","createTime":"2017-05-10T02:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T03:23:32.000Z","uid":13554,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa92f20092e8ef7c7e84ce51d50bc4355e22b380","tid":236732,"uid":13554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"因為我媽係印尼華僑<br />\n呢隻麵我真係由細食到大<br />\n大大話話麵食咗廿年<br />\n但都係食極都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次一食就會瘋狂咁扯啲麵入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8ae27b0843d8662efa488a1d6d039e16118895","tid":236732,"uid":49414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:46:18.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<br />\n加多兩條腸真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f81bcf75cfb93a3cb7658ea0920b5732240e03e","tid":236732,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"絕對同意"},{"pid":"ba6d68f628bef749220de5a33884e1ce25d3de71","tid":236732,"uid":25506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"樓主當三餐辣雞杯麵死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3030dad7f22b08ae8c8e76b18b35a6d3407a5d47","tid":236732,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊隻版本好食d 買百佳個d都ok? 你一次食幾pack"},{"pid":"1e0b667261aa175471c21be5436db9d77bb427b4","tid":236732,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"老穴認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6211d88938ff08b0de54745e9c9454634318ce","tid":236732,"uid":76362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"腎功能出問題未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心唔好食咁多<img sr